Class ScenariParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jimetevenard.xslt.ScenariParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SaxonScenariParser

    public abstract class ScenariParser
extends java.lang.Object
    A parser to deal with scenari xml File.
    Referer to the Scenari File schema
    By default, the implementation provided by the newInstance method is a SaxonScenariParser instance.
    Author:
    jetevenard
